body-ok-still-invalid: Is the body well-formed yet still invalid?
can-get: Can the method change to GET?
completed-later: Will the request be completed later?
feel-bad: Do you feel bad your code can't handle the request?
have-access: Does the user have access to the resource?
incompat-prev-request: Request incompatible with a previous request?
location-created: Was the Location created for the request?
method-handled: Is the HTTP method handled by the resource?
need-auth: Does the user need to authenticate?
redirect: Do you want to redirect the user to a new Location?
request-problem: Is there a problem with the request?
retry: Should the user Retry-After some time?
same-resource: Is it to the same resource at a new Location?
upstream-problem: Is it a problem with another server?
view-unchanged: Do you want the user's view to remain unchanged?
web-server: Am I implementing a web server?
